abstract: Sung Hyun Park takes second-round lead at United States Women's Open golf tournament; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: Park, a 22-year-old South Korean, had not competed before in the tournament but led stars like Lydia Ko at its halfway point.

headline.print_headline: A Newcomer Has the Lead at the U.S. Women’s Open
headline.main: Sung Hyun Park Leads U.S. Women’s Open
